gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Nuggets 111, Clippers 108
gameRecap.excerpt: Nikola Jokic put up 32 points, 16 rebounds and nine assists for the Nuggets as they defeated the Clippers, 111-108. Aaron Gordon added 20 points, five rebounds and five assists for the Nuggets in the victory, while Paul George tallied 35 points and seven rebounds for the Clippers in the losing effort. The Nuggets improve to 2-0 in West Group B play, 9-2 in the regular season, while the Clippers fall to 0-2 in West Group B play, 3-7 in the regular season.
